Privacy Policy for B-All Stars App

Last Updated: 31/01/2024

Thank you for choosing B-All Stars. This Privacy Policy is designed to inform you about the types of information we collect, how we use that information, and the choices you have regarding your personal data. By using our app, you agree to the terms outlined in this policy.

1. Information We Collect
1.1 Email Address
We collect and store the email address provided during the registration process for login purposes.
Your email address is the only personal information we collect.
2. Use of Personal Data
2.1 Account Management
Your email address is used for account creation, authentication, and account recovery purposes.
We do not use your email address for marketing or promotional purposes.
2.2 Service Improvement
We may use aggregated and anonymized data to analyze user behavior and improve the functionality and user experience of B-All Stars.
2.3 Account Deactivation
Your email address is retained only as long as your account is active. If you choose to deactivate your account, your email address will be deleted.
3. Third-Party Access
We do not share your personal information with third parties, except as required for the functionality of the B-All Stars app.
4. Data Security
We employ industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.
5. User Controls
5.1 Access and Correction
You have the right to access and correct your personal information. You can update your email address through the B-All Stars app's settings.
5.2 Account Deletion
You can request the deletion of your account and associated email address by contacting us at b-allstars@gmai.com.
6. Changes to this Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the updated policy on our website or through the B-All Stars app.
7. Contact Information
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at b-allstars@gmai.com

8. Applicability to UK and EU Users
This Privacy Policy complies with the data protection laws applicable to users in the United Kingdom and the European Union.
By using the B-All Stars app, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy.






